@host = http://localhost:8086
@json = application/json

### Health (GET /api/v1/health/alive)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/health/alive

### List Items (GET /api/v1/items)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/items

### Create Item (POST /api/v1/items) - valid
POST {{host}}/api/v1/items
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "My first item",
  "enabled": true,
  "tags": ["demo", "create"]
}

### Create Item (POST /api/v1/items) - invalid (missing body / required fields)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/items
Content-Type: {{json}}

### Get Item by ID (GET /api/v1/items/{id})
@itemId = item-1
GET {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}

### Replace Item (PUT /api/v1/items/{id}) - valid (PUT requires full object)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Replaced item name",
  "enabled": true,
  "tags": ["demo", "put"]
}

### Replace Item (PUT /api/v1/items/{id}) - invalid (missing required fields)
PUT {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "name": "Only name (invalid for PUT in this demo spec)"
}

### Patch Item (PATCH /api/v1/items/{id}) - valid (partial update)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "enabled": false,
  "tags": ["demo", "patch"]
}

### Patch Item (PATCH /api/v1/items/{id}) - invalid (missing body)
PATCH {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

### Delete Item (DELETE /api/v1/items/{id})
DELETE {{host}}/api/v1/items/{{itemId}}

### List Items again (GET /api/v1/items)
GET {{host}}/api/v1/items
